{"tid":2193304,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【台灣美女】非常養眼 台灣美女醫師「若玄」","createTime":"2020-09-07T17:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T08:22:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6b47d3c75054ce8ad3227a5625e0fc8746ca6680","tid":2193304,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"星期一，大家放完兩日假返咗成日工，黎到依家又唔瞓仲喺到碌電話，對對眼係唔好架你知道嗎？但我又唔係叫你即刻唔好睇落去，而係建議大家要睇啲對你對眼有益嘅嘢，例如睇下呢個台灣美金「若玄」咁啦！<br />\n<br />\n若玄畢業自台灣名校台大嘅醫學系，然後再去到美國進修，據佢IG所講，佢喺台灣同美國都有醫生執照，而根據佢係美國一間眼科專門學院嘅研究員，相信佢應該係眼科醫生之類，所以如果你對眼有事，就真係要去拍搵佢睇下，再唔係睇下佢啲相，相信都對大家對眼有幫助。事關兼職Model嘅若玄除咗外貌充滿氣質，仲有一對白滑長腿，一睇就知有外在有內涵，睇得多心情好啲，對眼又放鬆啲，有益身心呀！<br />\n<br />\nuuuuuu1s on Instagram"},{"pid":"6cad70d740486db1a0cd1063a89b8cd7bbb2bb9e","tid":2193304,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/object_pic/2020/9/7/447522cc235d13c5148e0c4e894c1330.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fobject_pic%2F2020%2F9%2F7%2F447522cc235d13c5148e0c4e894c1330.jpg&h=c59c701e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/object_pic/2020/9/7/a3c7f12c1007d63ed7e2c2525ba7a8b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fobject_pic%2F2020%2F9%2F7%2Fa3c7f12c1007d63ed7e2c2525ba7a8b2.jpg&h=65126721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/object_pic/2020/9/7/ae63572f70428dc0826c1c8d060a89b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fobject_pic%2F2020%2F9%2F7%2Fae63572f70428dc0826c1c8d060a89b4.jpg&h=afe9a314&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f478058a3fe7968151fc509a64d0c93a23244e5","tid":2193304,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T17:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"